{"tid":1427228,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[開始驚文宣]澳洲港生設「連儂牆」一周內兩度被毁　校方：不會縱容妨礙言論自由的行為","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:53:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"89bce8aa78776047f49c6a8e7af4f4fd00515660","tid":1427228,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:23:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190807/s00001/1565149104140/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e6%b8%af%e7%94%9f%e8%a8%ad%e3%80%8c%e9%80%a3%e5%84%82%e7%89%86%e3%80%8d%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e5%85%a7%e5%85%a9%e5%ba%a6%e8%a2%ab%e6%af%81-%e6%a0%a1%e6%96%b9-%e4%b8%8d%e6%9c%83%e7%b8%b1%e5%ae%b9%e5%a6%a8%e7%a4%99%e8%a8%80%e8%ab%96%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e7%9a%84%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190807%2Fs00001%2F1565149104140%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%2594%259f%25e8%25a8%25ad%25e3%2580%258c%25e9%2580%25a3%25e5%2584%2582%25e7%2589%2586%25e3%2580%258d%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%2591%25a8%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%25af%2581-%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e6%2596%25b9-%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%259c%2583%25e7%25b8%25b1%25e5%25ae%25b9%25e5%25a6%25a8%25e7%25a4%2599%25e8%25a8%2580%25e8%25ab%2596%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%2594%25b1%25e7%259a%2584%25e8%25a1%258c%25e7%2582%25ba&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Zw0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=6296a90d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190807%2Fs00001%2F1565149104140%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%2594%259f%25e8%25a8%25ad%25e3%2580%258c%25e9%2580%25a3%25e5%2584%2582%25e7%2589%2586%25e3%2580%258d%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%2591%25a8%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%25af%2581-%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e6%2596%25b9-%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%259c%2583%25e7%25b8%25b1%25e5%25ae%25b9%25e5%25a6%25a8%25e7%25a4%2599%25e8%25a8%2580%25e8%25ab%2596%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%2594%25b1%25e7%259a%2584%25e8%25a1%258c%25e7%2582%25ba&h=aa740df6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190807/s00001/1565149104140/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e6%b8%af%e7%94%9f%e8%a8%ad%e3%80%8c%e9%80%a3%e5%84%82%e7%89%86%e3%80%8d%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e5%85%a7%e5%85%a9%e5%ba%a6%e8%a2%ab%e6%af%81-%e6%a0%a1%e6%96%b9-%e4%b8%8d%e6%9c%83%e7%b8%b1%e5%ae%b9%e5%a6%a8%e7%a4%99%e8%a8%80%e8%ab%96%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e7%9a%84%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲昆士蘭大學的「連儂牆」繼周日（4日）被毁後，周二凌晨再次被蒙面人破壞。大學發言人表示，若能辨認出涉事者身分，將會採取「適當行動」，大學亦會加強「連儂牆」附近的保安。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昆士蘭大學的香港留學生上周五（2日）在校園設立「連儂牆」，以支持香港反修例運動及保護言論自由，吸引逾百名學生貼上便條留言。有份籌備「連儂牆」的香港姚姓（音譯）學生表示，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">周二凌晨有4名蒙面人大肆破壞「連儂牆」，把牆上所有內容撕去並棄於垃圾桶</span></span></strong>，而閉路電視已拍下他們，目前正確認4人的身分。<br />\n<br />\n昆士蘭大學發言人回應事件，強調大學不會縱容任何妨礙言論自由的行為，包括破壞「連儂牆」，而學生會已經將有關閉路電視片段交予校方，若調查後發現涉事者與大學有關，校方將會採取「適當行動」。警方已得悉事件，保安員亦將加強「連儂牆」一帶巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n姚姓學生表示任何人都可於「連儂牆」留言，他們亦歡迎中國留學生提出反對意見，但認為不能破壞牆將其他人「滅聲」。昆士蘭大學的「連儂牆」周日首次被毁，學生於翌日（5日）將牆修復，惟「連儂牆」當晚半夜再度被毁。姚姓學生強調暴力不會使他們卻步，並將繼續支持香港的民主及言論自由。<br />\n（衛報）"},{"pid":"972e5331f13bbdc0df0b47b385a06b1a8d290cae","tid":1427228,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"捉到踢埋佢出校就岩"},{"pid":"efbff3bc9d4964c9724466b0498b8c1fd8d91687","tid":1427228,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"972e5331f13bbdc0df0b47b385a06b1a8d290cae","tid":1427228,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"捉到踢埋佢出校就岩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":